/* =============================================================================
   {$name$}.css  —  UI stylesheet for the {$name$} app
   Generated by sdlos create [{$template$}].  Edit freely.
   Loaded automatically by jade_host after the jade scene is parsed.
   =============================================================================

   CSS cascade in sdlos
   --------------------
   • Selectors use the same id= and class= attributes as the jade markup.
   • Property names are camelCase in C++ / snake-case in CSS:
       background-color → backgroundColor    border-radius → borderRadius
   • Trailing "px" is stripped: padding: 12px == padding: 12
   • Inline jade attributes override CSS — use CSS for defaults, jade for
     structural values (flexGrow, width, …).
   • :hover rules are compiled to HoverEntry records and evaluated each frame
     against the pointer position — keep them cheap (colour swaps only).
   • :active rules drive the toggle-group radio state.  Each child of a node
     marked toggle-group="true" gets one :active entry.

   HiDPI / Retina
   --------------
   All geometry values are in LOGICAL pixels.  SDLRenderer multiplies by
   pixel_scale_x/y before writing to the GPU — you never need to know the
   physical resolution in CSS.  A div height: 44 is always 44 logical px,
   which maps to 88 physical px on a 2× Retina display.

   Design tokens (update here to retheme the whole app)
   ---------------------------------------------------
   Background  #0d0d12   — near-black canvas
   Surface     #ffffff0a — glass panel fill  (5% white)
   Accent      #6366f1   — indigo-500 (Tailwind)
   Text        #cccccc   — body text
   Dim text    #ffffff66 — 40% white label
   Separator   #ffffff18 — 10% white divider

   Camera-template layout notes
   ----------------------------
   Most per-panel sizing values (width, padding, gap, backgroundColor) are set
   inline in {$name$}.jade because the camera layout gives each column a unique
   fixed width.  Promote repeated inline attrs to class rules here once you
   start sharing them across nodes.
   ============================================================================= */

/* ── Filter / preset chips ────────────────────────────────────────────────── */

.preset {
    border-radius: 6;
    padding: 6;
}

.preset:hover {
    background-color: #ffffff1a;
}

/* ── +/– stepper buttons ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */

.param-btn {
    border-radius: 6;
}

.param-btn:hover {
    background-color: #ffffff40;
}

/* ── Dragnum value inputs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */

.param-val {
    border-radius: 6;
    background-color: #ffffff0a;
    color: #ffffffcc;
    font-size: 13;
}
